===Definitions===
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# [[bold]]; [[brave]]; [[daring]]
# to [[dare]] (to); to [[venture]] (to)
#: {{zh-x|我們 必須 敢 想，敢 說，敢 幹。|We must '''dare to''' think, speak up and act.}}
#: {{zh-x|他 不 敢 正 眼看 她。|He didn't '''dare to''' look at her in the face.}}
#: {{zh-x|在 那 個 風雨 交加 的 夜晚，很 少 有人 敢 出去。|Very few people '''ventured to''' go out on that stormy night.}}
# to be [[sure]]; to be [[certain]]; to [[bet]]; to [[presume]]
#: {{zh-x|敢 肯定|to be sure, to be certain}}
#: {{zh-x|敢 說|to be sure, to be certain}}
#: {{zh-x|我 敢 說 你 解決-不{bu}了{liǎo} 這.個 難題。|I '''bet''' you can't do this puzzle.}}
# {{lb|zh|polite}} may I [[venture]]
#: {{zh-x|敢 問|may I ask}}
#* {{quote-song|zh|year=1986|lyricist=lw:zh:閻肅<t:{{w|Yan Su}}>|composer=lw:zh:許鏡清<t:Xu Jingqing>|title=zh:敢問路在何方<t:Dare I ask where the road is?>}}
#*: {{zh-q|敢 問 路 在 何方？路 在 腳下。|'''Dare''' I ask where the road is? The road is beneath our feet.}}
# {{lb|zh|literary|or|Hokkien|Teochew|Taiwanese Hakka|rhetorical question}} [[can]] [[it]] be [[possible]] that; [[how]]
#: {{alti|zh|豈<tr:-><q:Hokkien>}}
#: {{zh-x|敢 通 按呢？|'''How''' could it be like this?|TW}}
# {{lb|zh|archaic|or|Xiamen Hokkien|Quanzhou Hokkien|&|Zhangzhou Hokkien}} [[perhaps]]
# {{lb|zh|Hokkien|Taiwanese Hakka}} {{n-g|Interrogative adverb, placed before the verb to create a yes-no question.}}
#: {{alti|zh|咁|甘|干|tr1=-|tr2=-|tr3=-}}
#: {{zh-x|你 敢 有閒？|Are you free?|TW}}

